Checkpoint: possibly, but i doubt it. Im sure they had to have set us down on the wrong mountain to test us. 

Damn it Donald! Think about it! They told me they were sick of my shit and you over heard the Captain say he was gonna get rid of me one way or another, so this is it! You saw how fast they left after we got off the chopper! They arent coming back for us! Period!

Absolutely! I mean, not to make you feel bad but they are a huge military complex with millions of people backing them, they could care less about what happens to an innocent life lost here or there! This is it man, game over!

No no no no, im not gonna die like this! Not here! Not now! Oh god why?!

Donald! Get a hold of yourself! This doesnt have to be the end for us! We can still survive. After all, this is what we are trained to do. Now we just have no one but ourselves to rely on now. 

...shit. Fuck! Okay. Youre right. We are trained for situations like this, just not the getting abandoned by the entirety of the military part. Fuck! What the hell are we gonna do? We are lost in the middle of no where and fuck knows how far the nearest civilization is. If we had been dropped in the right location, the nearest town would have been maybe a day's trip. And its dark! We are fucked so hard.

No we arent. You and i can do this. We just need to set up a small camp for now and get situated somewhere. After that we can sleep till morning and get our barings from there. Okay?
